<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-orange);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Building-Safety (BSA) Remediation</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Cladding and façade remediation on higher-risk buildings under the Building Safety Act 2022 — from intrusive survey and strip-out through to a compliant, fully documented replacement envelope, with the golden-thread records to prove it.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Building-Safety (BSA) Remediation →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Building-Safety (BSA) Remediation,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Cladding remediation</li><li>Intrusive surveys &amp; investigation</li><li>Strip-out &amp; replacement</li><li>Fire barriers &amp; cavity firestopping</li><li>Compliant re-clad to approved spec</li><li>Safety-case &amp; golden-thread records</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>Building Safety Act 2022 — higher-risk buildings</li><li>BS 8414 &amp; BR 135 — cladding fire performance</li><li>Building Regulations Part B (fire)</li><li>The golden thread of information</li><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work on higher-risk buildings under the Building Safety Act?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver cladding and façade remediation on higher-risk buildings under the Building Safety Act 2022, from intrusive survey and strip-out through to a compliant, documented replacement envelope.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you prove the remediated envelope is compliant?</summary><p>We install systems with fire performance assessed to BS 8414 against the BR 135 criteria, designed to meet Part B, and hand over a complete golden-thread records pack for the building's safety case.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you install fire barriers and cavity firestopping?</summary><p>Yes. Fire barriers and cavity firestopping are installed as part of the remediation scope, detailed correctly behind the new cladding and recorded for the safety case.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope overview</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/facade-cladding/">Façade &amp; Cladding</a><a class